		{
			description: [
				"Level 10 is your first real milestone. At this point your Cobblemon has learned several moves, gained meaningful stats, and you've started to understand how it fights."
				""
				"The fastest way to level up is consistent battling — wild Cobblemon give experience, and so do trainer battles if this pack enables them."
				""
				"&eTip: Rotate your party in and out of fights to share experience across your whole team.&r"
				""
				"Don't grind with just one — a deep, levelled bench is what carries you through harder chapters."
			]
