			dependencies: ["1000000000000023"]
			description: [
				"The &eCobblemon Capture XP&r mod rewards you with experience just for making catches — not just for battling."
				""
				"Higher-level Cobblemon award more capture XP, so it pays to push into tougher territory even when you're not grinding battles. Every successful catch is building your trainer level."
				""
				"500 capture XP is a solid early milestone — it means you've been actively expanding your collection rather than just battling the same species over and over."
				""
				"&7Tip: Higher-level Cobblemon give more capture XP — push into tougher areas.&r"
