		{
			dependencies: ["1000000000000023"]
			description: [
				"The &eCobblemon Counter&r mod tracks how many wild Cobblemon you've defeated. 25 defeats is a solid early target — it means you've been fighting consistently."
				""
				"Open the Cobblemon Counter with its keybind at any time to check your current stats. It tracks defeats, catches, and more depending on your pack's config."
				""
				"Getting into the habit of fighting (not just catching) will keep your team levelled and ready for the harder content ahead."
				""
				"&7Tip: Open the Cobblemon Counter with its keybind to track your battle stats.&r"
			]
