		{
			dependencies: ["1000000000000027"]
			description: [
				"Evolution transforms your Cobblemon into something stronger. Most Cobblemon evolve by reaching a certain level, but others require specific items, high friendship, or particular conditions."
				""
				"Check the &eCobblepedia&r entry for your Cobblemon to see exactly what it needs. Don't be surprised if your first evolution is straightforward — the more unusual requirements come later."
				""
				"Evolved Cobblemon gain better stats, learn new moves, and open up new strategies. Your team gets dramatically stronger once your first-stage catches start evolving."
				""
				"&7Tip: Check the Cobblepedia entry for the specific evolution requirement before grinding.&r"
			]
			id: "100000000000002F"
			min_width: 330
			rewards: [
