		}
		{
			dependencies: ["100000000000002F"]
			description: [
				"A fully evolved Cobblemon is as strong as that species gets. Final-stage Cobblemon have higher base stats, a full move pool, and are ready for serious fights."
				""
				"You can reach a fully evolved Cobblemon two ways: evolve one yourself through the full line, or find one already at its final stage in the wild. Both count."
				""
				"Some final-stage Cobblemon only appear in specific biomes or at higher levels in the wild — if you're finding evolution too slow, go exploring."
				""
				"&7Tip: Final-stage Cobblemon can be found in the wild — no need to always evolve from scratch.&r"
			]
