		{
			description: [
				"&eCobblemon Mike Skills&r adds a trainer progression system on top of standard Cobblemon gameplay. As you battle and catch, your trainer gains experience and earns Skill Points to invest."
				""
				"Skill Points let you specialise your playstyle:"
				"• Catch-rate branches improve your odds when throwing balls"
				"• Battle reward branches boost XP and item drops from wild fights"
				"• Exploration branches help with finding rare or specific Cobblemon"
				""
				"This is a separate progression track from your Cobblemon's levels — it's about you becoming a better trainer."
				""
				"&7Tip: Skill points are earned through battling and catching — just play normally.&r"
			]
