		{
			dependencies: ["1000000000000036"]
			description: [
				"Invest 3 points into the catch-rate branch of the Mike Skills tree. This directly improves your odds every time you throw a ball."
				""
				"Early in the game, failed catches are frustrating and expensive. A few points here pay for themselves quickly — especially when you're hunting rarer species that need multiple attempts."
				""
				"Combined with weakening Cobblemon before throwing, a levelled catch-rate skill makes a huge difference to how many balls you burn per session."
				""
				"&7Tip: Catch-rate skills can dramatically reduce wasted balls on rare spawns.&r"
			]
