			description: [
				"Now invest 3 points into the battle reward branch. Battle reward skills increase what you gain from wild fights — more XP for your team, better item drops, and potentially bonus resources."
				""
				"As your team grows stronger, you'll be fighting more and harder Cobblemon. Making each fight more rewarding keeps pace with the increasing difficulty."
				""
				"This is the skill branch for trainers who want to grind efficiently rather than just explore."
				""
				"&7Tip: Battle reward skills may increase item drops and XP from wild battles.&r"
