		{
			dependencies: ["1000000000000036"]
			description: [
				"Spread at least 1 point into 3 different skill branches. Before you specialise, it's worth experimenting — each branch reveals different bonuses and passive effects."
				""
				"You don't have to commit fully to one path early. A point in each of three branches costs only 3 skill points and gives you a sense of how each one plays before you double down."
				""
				"Some branches synergise well with others. The best trainers don't just focus — they adapt."
				""
				"&7Tip: Spread your points early to discover which playstyle fits you best.&r"
